    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know Rochedale well. I understand the buyer profile, what motivates the catchment-driven family decision, and how to position a property to attract genuine competition from across the southeastern corridor.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Rochedale's recent transformation has been one of the most significant in Brisbane's south. The masterplanned estates around Rochedale Village have delivered a deep base of modern family homes that consistently attract upgraders out of older south Brisbane addresses. The Rochedale State School catchment is the gravitational anchor for many family buyers, and properties that fall clearly within the catchment with confirmed school access regularly outperform comparable homes that sit just outside it. The eastern pockets retain larger acreage-style blocks that appeal to a different buyer entirely, and that internal variation is one of the reasons campaign positioning matters here.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Rochedale Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Southeastern Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229; border-radius:16px;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Strong Catchment Demand</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Modern family estates</p>
